Enclosing class:
MissionManager
public static enum MissionManager.MissionEvent extends Enum<MissionManager.MissionEvent>
An enum storing all possible events that the MissionManager's EventHandler should listen to and trigger. To add a listener to the MissionManager, create a new MissionManager.MissionEvent enum value, and add a listener for the Enum.name() of the enum value.
